Damage Immunities: bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical weapons
Innate Spellcasting: They empyrean's innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC 23, + 15 to hit with spell attacks). It can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components: At will: greater restoration, pass without trace, water breathing, water walk 1/day each: commune, dispel evil and good, earthquake, fire storm, plane shift (self only)
Legendary Resistance (3/day): If the empyrean fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead
Magic Resistance: The empyrean has advantage on saving throws against spells and other effects
Magic Weapons: The empyrean's weapon attacks are magical
